{"featured_counts":2,"common_counts":23,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/559569774/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=2\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/559569774/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=0\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":16},"data":[{"id":566519781,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566519781","content":"惊闻又一高中生自称能够证明哥德巴赫猜想，深感长江后浪推前浪。\u003cbr\u003e看了众多答案，许多答案几近冷嘲热讽。很多人都在笑，我却笑不出来，眼泪往肚子里咽。因为，一个国家没有人才是可怕的，有人才没被发现是可悲的，但发现了人才却对其进行嘲讽就是可耻了。\u003cbr\u003e但是，证明不是乱证，猜想不是乱猜。连陈景润老先生都说，只用初等数论的知识是无法解决哥德巴赫猜想的；但你如果一定要告诉我们你可以“骑自行车上月球”，结果我们看到你是骑自行车上了一个写着“月”字的球，那么你作为证明者是要向本国人民谢罪的。\u003cbr\u003e不管结果怎样，我都希望题主能够给各位一个交代，毕竟证明哥德巴赫猜想是具有世界级影响力的事情，不可儿戏。就算题主失败了，也不要气馁。有勇气去证明哥德巴赫猜想的，想必已有比较扎实的数学功底和强大的数学思维。希望题主日后苦练七十二变，笑对八十一难。\u003cbr\u003e说到八十一难，我就想起我国四大名著之一《西游记》。明年下半年，中美合拍，正式开机，弘扬中华文化，文体两开花，多多关注。","featured":true,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545916058,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"83e84e3d4c12f3cf51feed8f9bbf077b","url_token":"mu-yi-5-47","name":"木易","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/83e84e3d4c12f3cf51feed8f9bbf077b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":89,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":9,"chi